[13.914574, "o", "\r\n"]
[13.918491, "o", "┌─ The three commands ─────────────────────────────────────────────┐\r\n│  /dev    9-phase pipeline — features, refactors, design spec   │\r\n│  /fix    5-phase fast path — bug fixes with TDD + security     │\r\n│  /quick  Scout → Act — small scoped tasks, lowest tokens       │\r\n└────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\r\n"]
[17.924976, "o", "\r\n$ npx aicrew --help | sed -n \"/AFTER INSTALL/,+7p\"\r\n"]
[18.257238, "o", "AFTER INSTALL\r\n  Claude Code — daily slash commands:\r\n    /dev             — full development pipeline (bug fix, feature, refactor)\r\n    /fix             — fast bug fix (3 questions, no ceremony)\r\n    /quick           — Scout → Act (graph-first, Karpathy guardrails)\r\n    /conclude        — save session learnings to memory\r\n    /brainstorm  /handoff  /session  /lean   (/normal = /lean off)\r\n    Maintenance (rare): /update-skills  /harness-audit  /benchmark\r\n"]
[21.280346, "o", "\r\n$ cat docs/demo-pipeline.txt\r\n"]
[21.285006, "o", "═══ aicrew pipelines (at a glance) ═══\r\n\r\n/dev  — 9 phases\r\n  Intake → Research → Brainstorm → Design → Implement (TDD)\r\n  → Tests → Security → Audit → Conclude\r\n  Use: features, refactors, multi-system changes\r\n\r\n/fix  — 5 phases\r\n  Bug Analysis → Implement (TDD) → Tests → Security → Conclude\r\n  Use: known bugs — TDD + security, no ceremony\r\n\r\n/quick — Scout → Act\r\n  Graph-first discovery → surgical implementation\r\n  Use: rename, tweak, small scoped additions\r\n\r\nToken (illustrative): graph query ~500 tok  vs  repo grep ~80K tok\r\n  aicrew benchmark — repo-specific estimates\r\n"]
